By Uche Metuh How do I get a US visa from Nigeria to have my baby in America? The US embassy doesn’t reject Visa applications for pregnant Nigerian women. They reject their applications because they lied about something on the application like: What happens if you’re pregnant & applying for a Visa is just that your situation has now changed: Hence, the US embassy will assess you differently. Find out what they need! Give the US embassy what they need & you’d be fine! Source: Quora